{"tid":2151950,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[忍到笑先入]  陳偉霆自認普通話唔掂  慘被楊冪「收嗲啦你」","createTime":"2020-08-11T16:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T06:44:20.000Z","uid":192075,"like":4,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2d14ffa0b739023d4d7117be70c07eb4d1d3c9","tid":2151950,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"近年積極在內地發展的陳偉霆（William）事業風生水起，戲劇作品不斷，而且合作過的演員都是一線小生花旦，可見他人氣強勁。近日William與楊冪在橫店趕拍2021年的年度壓軸劇集《斛珠夫人》，今次已經是兩人第三次合作，自然默契十足，但日前William接受訪問時，就透露被楊冪嫌棄普通話太差，令他大受打擊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v7v2v3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v7v2v3.jpg&h=f201c6a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">近日陳偉霆（William）與楊冪在橫店趕拍劇集《斛珠夫人》。</span><br />\n<br />\nWilliam在2013年開始進軍內地市場，翌年憑着大熱劇集《古劍奇譚》而人氣急升，之後他再參演多部劇集包括《老九門》、《醉玲瓏》、《南方有喬木》等，晉升成為一線男星。不過在內地發展多年的William依然有死穴，就是他的「港式普通話」，更多次被取笑，William日前在訪問中自爆被拍檔楊冪打擊：「她說了一句話<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">『其實我都聽不懂你在說什麼，你其實不用背詞』</span></span>，你知道我多難受嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TJGwM0p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJGwM0p.png&h=eb91cb90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g868PdL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg868PdL.png&h=335d1f92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9B0BdFq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9B0BdFq.png&h=7f01fa71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWilliam近年接拍了不少古裝劇，但在講對白方面依然很吃力：「比如說裏面有一大堆的台詞，我很用心背，背完之後，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">『你在說什麼呀？反正都聽不懂你，要不用廣東話說一遍？』</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o5oZVXp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo5oZVXp.png&h=f93b2b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實William似乎對自己的「港普」一直耿耿於懷，早前他為內地綜藝節目《認真的嘎嘎們》擔任導師時，有一位學員錘錘用港式普通話講述自己的經歷，結果William反應敏感：「你是取笑我嗎？」更質問對方：「你是歧視我嗎？」言語間似乎相當介意。不過William的粉絲就力撐偶像，認為他的普通話講得愈來愈好，進步很大！<br />\n<br />\n原片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bp_8qHL55Mc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fbp_8qHL55Mc&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=6c285270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bp_8qHL55Mc</a><br />\n<br />\n15:20 開始被肥妹笑<br />\n之後再比兩個大陸仔插多吓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喊戲又比人笑<br />\n連講句對白都比楊冪「收嗲啦你」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解佢可以帶比人咁多歡樂嘅<br />\n<br />\n我懷疑果吓人哋心諗 <br />\n你再講我會忍唔住笑NG<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37be7229c6dd59fdc6444753d610f141011182df","tid":2151950,"uid":38884,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:52:57.000Z","msg":"俾人笑億億聲收入"},{"pid":"9f80631b6dbdfdcf61cbdb7951cb5413977c3e25","tid":2151950,"uid":326700,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"弱智仔 唔識唔走撚去學 仲以為人歧視<br />\n抵你俾香港人弱智"},{"pid":"668abf0ba6c63eff4bbfd302e8b9e32e48e9d891","tid":2151950,"uid":192075,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"37be7229c6dd59fdc6444753d610f141011182df","tid":2151950,"uid":38884,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:52:57.000Z","msg":"俾人笑億億聲收入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:56:06.000Z","msg":"八年時間普通話都仲咁<br />\n最好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae56d95397ee2ca47f8d0953e07ab38529254b15","tid":2151950,"uid":361751,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UeRPGN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UeRPGN.png&h=38833bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTake左野？"},{"pid":"ef11c9fdccc9a10152b42ce6f74ef18d60e8d08e","tid":2151950,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae56d95397ee2ca47f8d0953e07ab38529254b15","tid":2151950,"uid":361751,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"ci